{
  "stem": "14251.1",
  "chunk_idx": 3,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 3.0,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "They tried carefully to scrape some of this stuff together to put it back, but it was impossible.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "But-- and then, I only remember him saying goodbye to me when I had to leave them-- when the three of us had to be split up to go into hiding.",
      "word_count": 31
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And other than that, I really don't remember him.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Well, we had to go to the train station in Berlin, which is still in existence, I believe.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "It's Anhalter Bahnhof.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And it was a main station, huge, with many, many tracks for cattle cars, for passenger, for express, this and that.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And we stood outside, up on the sidewalk with steps going down.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And he sort of knelt down by me and said things that I don't remember.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "I was to go with this, quote, 'nice lady.' And that was that.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "By that time of course, I was already used to living without him or without my mother just about all the time.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "That was in '43.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "June, I believe.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Since my birthday is in June, I guess I must have been five.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Or maybe a week or two or three before I was five.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Yes.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "As a matter of fact, I wore these today because I thought he should be here in some form.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And the watch is running, although, it's never been cleaned or repaired.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "I set it this morning, wound it up-- it's a manual wind, of course-- and it's running perfectly.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And the ring has his initials on it for Ernst Goldstein.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And his brother had one that was TG for Theodore Goldstein.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "I think their father had these made [PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] for their 16th birthdays or something.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "But he always wore it.",
      "word_count": 5
    }
  ],
